[
  {
    "startTime": 0.3,
    "endTime": 2.1999999999999997,
    "text": "So do you recognize any of these men?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.3,
    "endTime": 6.583,
    "text": "I was hiding in the bathroom stall so I didn't see his face, but I heard him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.583,
    "endTime": 8.2,
    "text": "He was singing along to the music at the bar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.4,
    "endTime": 9.1,
    "text": "Do you remember what he was singing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.4,
    "endTime": 13.293,
    "text": "I think it was that song \"I want it that way\"?  - Backstreet Boys. I'm familiar."
